# First Medical Center LLC — Application Details

## Overview

| Item | Detail |
|---|---|
| **App Name** | `booking-system` (v0.1.0) |
| **Company** | First Medical Center LLC |
| **Framework** | Next.js 16.1.6 (App Router) |
| **Language** | TypeScript 5 |
| **Frontend** | React 19.2.3, Tailwind CSS 4 |
| **Hosting** | Azure (via GitHub → `main` branch auto-deploy) |
| **Repository** | `github.com/alfrinantony/booking-first-medical-center` |

---

## Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **UI Components** | React + Tailwind CSS + Lucide Icons |
| **State Management** | Zustand 5 (persisted stores with `zustand/middleware`) |
| **Form Handling** | React Hook Form + Zod validation |
| **Payments** | Stripe (JS + React SDK) |
| **File Storage** | Azure Blob Storage (`@azure/storage-blob`) |
| **Email** | Nodemailer |
| **Date Utilities** | date-fns |
| **Voice/AI** | OpenAI (Whisper STT + GPT) |

---

## Storage Architecture

### 1. Client-Side Storage (Zustand Persisted Stores → `localStorage`)

All application data is persisted in the browser's `localStorage` via Zustand's `persist` middleware. Each store has its own key:

| Store File | localStorage Key | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| [billing-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/billing-store.ts) | `billing-store` | Invoices, invoice sequences |
| [bookings-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/bookings-store.ts) | `bookings-store` | All appointment bookings |
| [clients-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/clients-store.ts) | `clients-store` | Client / patient records |
| [clinics-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/clinics-store.ts) | `clinics-store` | Branch/clinic configurations |
| [contracts-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/contracts-store.ts) | `contracts-store` | Branch contracts |
| [customer-auth-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/customer-auth-store.ts) | `customer-auth-store` | Customer login/registration |
| [doctors-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/doctors-store.ts) | `doctors-store` | Doctor profiles |
| [services-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/services-store.ts) | `services-store` | Services catalog |
| [packages-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/packages-store.ts) | `packages-store` | Treatment packages |
| [accounting-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/accounting-store.ts) | `accounting-store` | Chart of accounts, transactions, invoices |
| [hr-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/hr-store.ts) | `hr-store` | Employee records |
| [hr-documents-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/hr-documents-store.ts) | `hr-documents-store` | Employee documents metadata |
| [hr-leave-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/hr-leave-store.ts) | `hr-leave-store` | Leave records |
| [hr-payroll-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/hr-payroll-store.ts) | `hr-payroll-store` | Payslips, salary records |
| [hr-letters-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/hr-letters-store.ts) | `hr-letters-store` | HR letters & templates |
| [hr-recruitment-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/hr-recruitment-store.ts) | `hr-recruitment-store` | Recruitment candidates |
| [inbox-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/inbox-store.ts) | `inbox-store` | Internal messages |
| [logs-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/logs-store.ts) | `logs-store` | Audit logs |
| [loyalty-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/loyalty-store.ts) | `loyalty-store` | Loyalty points program |
| [notification-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/notification-store.ts) | `notification-store` | Notification settings |
| [promo-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/promo-store.ts) | `promo-store` | Promo codes |
| [settings-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/settings-store.ts) | `settings-store` | App settings |
| [users-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/users-store.ts) | `users-store` | Staff / admin accounts |
| [verification-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/verification-store.ts) | `verification-store` | OTP / email verification |
| [call-agent-summary-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/call-agent-summary-store.ts) | `call-agent-summaries` | Voice call agent logs |
| [resources-store.ts](file:///c:/AntiGravityWorks/Booking%20First%20Medical%20Center/booking-system/lib/resources-store.ts) | `resources-store` | Shared resources |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> All business data currently lives in **browser localStorage** via Zustand persisted stores. This means data is local to each browser/device and is not synced across users. This is suitable for a single-user/demo setup but would need a database backend (e.g., Azure SQL, Cosmos DB) for production multi-user access.

### 2. Azure Blob Storage (File/Document Storage)

Used for uploading and storing **binary files** (PDFs, images, scanned documents).

| Setting | Value |
|---|---|
| **Service** | Azure Blob Storage |
| **Container** | `fmc-documents` |
| **SDK** | `@azure/storage-blob` v12.31 |
| **Connection** | Via `AZURE_STORAGE_CONNECTION_STRING` env var |

**Blob Path Structure:**

| Category | Path Pattern | Example |
|---|---|---|
| HR Employee Docs | `hr/employees/{empId}/{category}/{timestamp}-{file}` | `hr/employees/emp-001/passport/1709-scan.pdf` |
| Recruitment Docs | `hr/recruitment/candidates/{id}/{type}/{timestamp}-{file}` | `hr/recruitment/candidates/cand-01/cv/resume.pdf` |
| Accounting Receipts | `accounting/transactions/{txnId}-{timestamp}-{file}` | `accounting/transactions/txn-01-1709-receipt.jpg` |
| Product Registration | `products/registrations/{timestamp}-{file}` | `products/registrations/1709-cert.pdf` |
| HR Letters | `letters/{letterId}-{timestamp}-{file}` | `letters/ltr-01-1709-offer.pdf` |

### 3. Session Storage

| Key | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `adminUser` | Stores logged-in admin user object for session |

