## Environment Variables

| Variable | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | OpenAI API for Whisper STT + GPT voice agent |
| `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY` | Stripe server-side payment processing |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` | Stripe client-side checkout |
| `AZURE_STORAGE_CONNECTION_STRING` | Azure Blob Storage access |
| `AZURE_STORAGE_CONTAINER` | Blob container name (default: `fmc-documents`) |
| `EMIRATES_ID_TOOLKIT_URL` | Emirates ID card reader endpoint |
| `VOICE_AGENT_TRANSFER_WEBHOOK_URL` | Voice agent human transfer webhook |
| `CALL_AGENT_API_KEY` | External call agent API authentication |

