| Whisper | `/api/whisper/*` | Speech-to-text processing |
| TTS | `/api/tts/*` | Text-to-speech |
| Messages | `/api/messages/*` | Messaging endpoints |
| Webhooks | `/api/webhooks/*` | External webhook handlers |
